; Test automated transaction with inline check and assert

= /^Expenses:Food/
    check amount > 0
    (Expenses:Tax)    (amount * 0.10)

2024/01/01 Payee
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Checking

test bal
            $-100.00  Assets:Checking
             $110.00  Expenses
             $100.00    Food
              $10.00    Tax
--------------------
              $10.00
end test

